
"Deal with it."
"You know what instead of Vic getting pushed off of the stage tonight it's going to be you." Mike said glaring at him.
"No, no I will break your drums or something."
"No! My dad got me those!" He whined and I rolled my eyes and looked over at Kellin who was watching the two idiots amused. He looks so adorable, smiling like that.
"This is even better than t.v." He whispered to me and I nodded not looking away from him.
"Yeah it is."